data.description: This beautifully maintained home is now available for you and your family to rent during your time here in Killeen! A lovely three bedroom home with Office, boasts additional rooms in the converted garage that can be used as A Home school, Yoga Studio, craft room or Office!, and offers a large backyard! Upon entering you are greeted with beautiful hardwood floors, and an open concept floor-plan that showcases a large wood burning fireplace, eat in kitchen, with island and flooded with tons of Sunshine! Upstairs you will find a large second living space, and all three bedrooms, including the large Master bedroom, that boasts an exquisite Master Bath and a large Balcony, for the perfect retreat! The home is equipped with BOSE surround sound speakers throughout for the perfect added touch! Call Soldiers First to get a private tour today!
